1- Ordered Lists

<ol>                                  //defines ordered list
  <li> Wake up </li>
  <li> Brush teeth </li>                 //defines each item list
  <li> Have breakfast </li>
</ol>


2- Unordered Lists

<ul>                               //define unordered list
  <li> Milk </li>
  <li> Bread </li>                   //defines each item list
  <li> Eggs </li>
</ul>


3- Description Lists

<dl>                                //defines description list
  <dt> HTML </dt>
  <dd> HyperText Markup Language </dd>

  <dt> CSS </dt>                    //defines term                
  <dd> Cascading Style Sheets </dd>        //define description 
</dl>
